TASK: refactor

TARGET: [directory or file path]

CREATE: [new files if splitting, or none]

PURPOSE: [what this refactor achieves — must be a concrete improvement, not "clean up"]

BEHAVIOR:
- [step 1: specific mechanical transformation]
- [step 2: what moves where]
- [step 3: how references are updated]
- update all imports that reference moved code
- update barrel/index exports

CONSTRAINTS:
- NO behavior changes — pure mechanical restructuring
- all existing tests must pass without modification
- no new features smuggled in
- no renaming unless specified
- every moved piece must have a clear destination
- if in doubt about where something goes, ASK

DONE_WHEN:
- lint passes
- types pass
- ALL existing tests pass (not just targeted ones)
- no behavior change (same public API)
- git diff shows only moves/renames, no logic changes
